  exact: external_exports.boolean().optional().describe("B123: REQUIRE fast-runner (no daemon fallback). Preserves user-supplied durationMs verbatim \u2014 needed for slow precise swipes on UIDatePicker wheels and similar momentum-sensitive UIs. Fails with EXACT_REQUIRES_FAST_RUNNER if fast-runner unavailable instead of silently degrading.")
